  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个文档处理管道的状态图。系统里有三个基础设施组件：Etcd集群做元数据、Redis缓存做队列、还有一个负载均衡器。文档从上传开始，经过PENDING、PROCESSING，最后到READY或者FAILED。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "PENDING",
        "PROCESSING",
        "READY",
        "FAILED",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。PENDING状态是文档刚上传的时候吗？还有，PROCESSING到READY和FAILED的触发条件分别是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PENDING",
        "PROCESSING",
        "READY",
        "FAILED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，PENDING是上传初始化后，元数据存在Etcd里，二进制文件放S3/MinIO，任务进Redis队列。PROCESSING是Worker取到任务后做文本提取、分块、生成向量。成功就进READY，失败就进FAILED——失败的情况通常跟负载均衡器有关，比如Worker节点故障。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PENDING",
        "PROCESSING",
        "READY",
        "FAILED",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主线画出来：从Etcd集群开始，到PENDING，Worker接手后进入PROCESSING，然后分支到READY或FAILED。我在PENDING、PROCESSING、READY、FAILED旁边加上注释说明具体在做什么。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "PENDING",
        "PROCESSING",
        "READY",
        "FAILED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还需要两个重要的回环：READY和FAILED都可以回到PENDING，这是用户触发的重新处理请求。另外，每个状态都应该能删除文档——READY的文档从Redis缓存删除，FAILED的从负载均衡器清理，PENDING的直接回Etcd集群清理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "READY",
        "FAILED",
        "PENDING",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下删除的流向：READY指向Redis缓存，FAILED指向负载均衡器，PENDING指回Etcd集群。重新处理的请求都是回到PENDING状态，对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "READY",
        "FAILED",
        "PENDING",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。还有FAILED状态的注释要特别强调：error_message字段会保存失败原因，这样用户知道为什么出错，也方便排查。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FAILED",
        "error_message"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。四个状态都有详细注释：PENDING说明元数据和存储位置，PROCESSING说明Worker的具体操作，READY说明向量入库和RAG可用性，FAILED说明错误信息和可重试特性。所有状态转换和删除流向也都画好了。",
